  "texts": [
    "When AICC extracts more (positive ratios), the preference reverses: AICC wins 75-98%, with preference increasing monotonically with the ratio.Weighting the bin-wise win rates by the population distribution in Figure 3, AICC achieves a 72.0% overall win rate.",
    "This indicates that the additional content preserved by MinerU-HTML is overwhelmingly judged as valuable main content rather than noise, reflecting both higher recall and maintained precision relative to heuristic extraction.To understand failure modes, we manually examine cases from the extreme and near-zero bins, with examples provided in Appendix F:1.",
    "[0.9, 1.0]: AICC longer than TfCC: Most AICC documents are preferred.",
    "For example, Figure 17 shows a case where Trafilatura drops much of the main body content.2.",
    "[-0.1, 0.1]: Similar length: Even at similar lengths, AICC can be superior."
  ]
